    pipeline: "Approximately 2,100 students. Williams sends graduates to Harvard, Yale, Stanford, MIT, Oxford, Cambridge, and other elite graduate programs at one of the highest rates of any liberal arts college in the nation. Major recruiters include Goldman Sachs, Morgan Stanley, McKinsey & Company, Bain & Company, Boston Consulting Group, BlackRock, Bridgewater Associates, Blackstone, KKR, Google, Meta, and leading academic, nonprofit, and public-policy institutions. Williams has one of the highest per-capita placement rates into finance and investment management of any undergraduate institution in America.",

